The upstream system prompt was adapted from an Electron host model (artifact-
tag wrapping, EDITMODE / TWEAKS protocols, virtual-FS device frames, TypeScript
keyword-routing composer) to a Claude Code skill model (direct .html file
output, Read-on-demand reference files, frontmatter trigger).

No binary assets, model weights, or runtime code are included from upstream;
this repository ships the prompt-layer adaptation only.
